<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-8">
      <div class="mt-3 mb-3">
        <div class="media">
          <img class="mr-3 rounded-circle" src="<%= image_url("brandon.jpg")%>" width="72" alt="Brandon Anderson">
          <div class="media-body">
            <span class="font-weight-bold">Can you tell me what happened exactly?</span>
            <br>
            Be detailed as possible.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%= form_with(model: @incident, local: true, url: wizard_path, id: "incident-form", html: {"data-parsley-validate" => ""}) do |form| %>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label>How did it start? You:</label>
          <%= form.select :category, Incident::CATEGORIES, {prompt: false, include_blank: false}, class: "form-control"  %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Then what happened?</label>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-link btn-sm text-info" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#incidentExampleModal">
            See an example
          </button>
          <%= form.text_area :text, class: "form-control", placeholder: "I was stopped by the cops when…", rows: 5, required: true, "data-parsley-required-message": "We need to know what happened with the police in your own words." %>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="progress mt-4 mb-3" style="height: 4px;">
            <div class="progress-bar bg-danger" role="progressbar" style="width: 40%" aria-valuenow="40" aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100"></div>
          </div>
          <%= form.submit "Next", class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg text-uppercase btn-block" %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>  
  </div>
</div>


<!-- Modal -->
<div class="modal fade" id="incidentExampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="incidentExampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="incidentExampleModalLabel">Example</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        I was stopped by police a couple years ago while driving. The reason the cop gave was that he got reports of my car being stolen. Well, it was my car and I didn’t report it stolen. So, I’m not sure who reported it stolen.
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>